WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.900
Did you know we publish cheatsheets for data science tools?

00:00:02.900 --> 00:00:04.320
And I mean literal cheatsheets.

00:00:04.320 --> 00:00:06.660
We even print them out for PositConf.

00:00:06.660 --> 00:00:09.680
Cheatsheets are quick reference guides for Posit's tools and packages.

00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:14.000
Say you're building a plot in ggplot2 and need a reminder of the aesthetic properties.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:15.200
Just pull up the cheatsheet.

00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:17.280
Take a look at all the aesthetic properties.

00:00:17.280 --> 00:00:18.879
Did you forget how to add a label?

00:00:18.879 --> 00:00:20.400
Alright, geom text.

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:22.719
Keep tweaking until you've built the graph of your dreams.

00:00:22.719 --> 00:00:26.700
And cheatsheets are perfect for discovering handy features you didn't even know existed.

00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:29.340
Some of them are available in other languages too.

00:00:29.340 --> 00:00:31.139
So what cheatsheet do you want to see next?

